ds.time
Class Time24

java.lang.Object
  ds.time.Time24
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Time24>
public class Time24
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Time24>, java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable

An instance of the class stores time in hour and minute units where hour is in the range 0 to 23 and minute is in the range 0 to 59.

See Also:
